        <hr noshade size="2" color="#545A7D">
        
         up until around level 30 you can safely lifetap tank with your pet, back around 24 or so I would pull a golra in TD, sic pet, then unload spells until I got agro'd on. Then I'd lifetap whatever damage I took.</P><P>Post 50 you can really only do it against mobs that are slowed (and even that will tear you down fast).</P><P>At your level though feel free to tank all you want. ;)</P><P>Keep your hp total as high as you can, and get used to keeping it there. HP is your life in more ways than one.</P><P><a href="http://tru7h.org/absor/" target="_blank">http://tru7h.org/absor/</a> -  ask absor anything!<BR><a href="http://xzzy.org/ereet/" target="_blank">http://xzzy.org/ereet/</a><a href="#top"><img src="icon_go_up.gif" height="15" width="15" border="0" align="right" alt="Go to Top of Page"></a></font></td>
