         Here's what I find handiest to do.</P><P>Set your escape level.  Eg, mana suffcient to cast Gate, FD, HS, etc, HP enough to run out...you get the picture.</P><P>Rule #1  Death = loss of exp = loss of time = loss of exp efficancy = bad.</P><P>Rule #2  NEVER go below your escape level rule you set.</P><P>Rule #3  If you go below your escape level rule enough times = Death.  See Rule #1.</P><P>Rule #4  If you find yourself dying a lot.  Revamp your escape level rule.</P><P></P><P><a href="http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=95266" target="_blank">Kuotat Smith</a><BR><s>Warlock</s> Witch<BR>Mithaniel Marr<a href="#top"><img src="icon_go_up.gif" height="15" width="15" border="0" align="right" alt="Go to Top of Page"></a></font></td>
