         When I fought in dreadlands solo (46-49) I just medded to 1 bubble and about 3 pixels.  That was all I needed.  Go out and pull with leach(or some other low aggro thing) then sick pet on thing when I came back to fighting spot.  Dark, fear, fear again when breaks and watch pet rip the living crap out of anything I pulled.  Only times I ever got in trouble were when I had freak resist rates and I was oom before anything stuck.</P><P>Ash nazg durbatuluk<BR>Ash nazg gimbatul<BR>Ash nazg thrakatuluk,<BR>Agh burzum-ishi krimpatul.<a href="#top"><img src="icon_go_up.gif" height="15" width="15" border="0" align="right" alt="Go to Top of Page"></a></font></td>
